videos.headline: Granderson's interception sets up TD
videos.description: Carl Granderson leaps and takes the ball out of the air, stiff arms a defender and returns it 37 yards. Wyoming scores on a 1-yard touchdown run three plays later.

videos.headline: Allen runs a mile just for 8 yards
videos.description: Josh Allen escapes numerous defenders, runs in circles and somehow gains eight yards on the play.

videos.headline: Fort takes handoff in for 2nd TD
videos.description: Austin Fort finds the endzone for the second time in the first half as Wyoming takes a 21-0 lead over New Mexico.

videos.headline: Allen finds Fort for 11-yard TD
videos.description: Josh Allen connects with Austin Fort for the second time through the air and third time overall for Fort.

videos.headline: Allen throws 4th TD
videos.description: Josh Allen finds John Okwoli for the 19-yard touchdown as Wyoming breaks open a 35-0 lead.

videos.headline: Allen finds Johnson for 5th TD
videos.description: Josh Allen proves why he is a highly touted prospect with his fifth touchdown pass, this time to C.J. Johnson.

videos.headline: Allen impresses in Wyoming's 42-3 victory over New Mexico
videos.description: Josh Allen tosses four touchdown passes and impresses in Wyoming's blow out win over New Mexico.
